OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with rain at first. The
OL,6,Frain will clear as a few bright spells
OL,7,Fdevelop in the morning. Scattered
OL,8,Fshowers soon follow from the west,
OL,9,Fthese wintry on the hills.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers, wintry on the hills,
OL,12,Fcontinue through the evening before
OL,13,Fclearing from the east by midnight.
OL,14,FThis will leave the rest of the night
OL,15,Fdry and cold with clear periods.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FDry and bright becoming
OL,18,Fcloudy from the morning with outbreaks
OL,19,Fof rain and hill snow in the
OL,20,Fafternoon. The wind will strengthen
OL,21,Ftowards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
