OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,6,Frain, hill snow and gales clear Sunday
OL,7,Fmorning, leaving a few afternoon
OL,8,Fshowers. Mostly dry but cloudy Monday
OL,9,Fand Tuesday.
